{
  "stem": "24651.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But he said that he was awakened at 5 o'clock in the morning hearing shots, and shooting, or explosions, or-- and he turned on the radio.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he heard that Germany had invaded Poland.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "At that point, my father took me, and my mother, and my sister to my other grandparents' house.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I'm not sure exactly at what point, whether he waited days, or probably you know, the next day or whatever.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But he returned to Nowy Targ.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so I stayed with my grandparents, my mother, and my sister.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And at that point, my grandfather loaded up the wagon-- horse and wagon.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "My grandfather was in the-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] he traded hay and everything to do with horses.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He had that kind of a shop.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So he loaded up the wagon with the family-- my aunt and uncle-- two aunts and uncles, my mother and myself, my sister-- and as many belongings as we could fit into this wagon and two horses.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we joined a caravan of people heading eastward.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And there were people walking, riding on horses or any which-- bicycles.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we were traveling for days and days and days, heading toward Russia.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "During this travel, I do remember a-- an airplane, a German plane.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I think it was German.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It may not have been a German, but an airplane that was shot down and fell out of the sky.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We were being shot at.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "There were bullets.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And we-- often, we had to get out of the wagon and hide in ditches and wait till the shooting stopped.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Sometimes the roads were blocked.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Sometimes bridges were out and we couldn't get across.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And so we would have to go across the river.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And so this continued until-- until we reached Russia.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
